## CI/CD integration

See [AgentOps Setup Guide](../docs/agentops-setup.md) for CI/CD configuration.

After CI/CD is configured:
1. Push all code to `main` — triggers deployment to staging
2. Create a `release` branch from `main` — triggers deployment to prod
3. PRs to `main` validate the bundle and run tests against the test target
{{- end }}

## Modifying resources

Edit the YAML files in this directory, then validate and deploy:

```bash
databricks bundle validate -t dev
databricks bundle deploy -t dev
```

Run `databricks bundle schema` to see the full schema of available resource types and properties.

